data.title: The Alfred Hitchcock Wiki
data.text:
Warner Bros. Entertainment Inc. is an American producer of film, television, and music entertainment.

One of the major film studios, it is a subsidiary of Time Warner, with its headquarters in Burbank, California and New York. Warner Bros. has several subsidiary companies, including Warner Bros. Studios and Warner Bros. Pictures.
